summary: Unpopular opinion but... I love Sansa and I love dany. Everyone wants them to be against each other and I totally see why but...
body:
Unpopular opinion but… I love Sansa and I love dany. Everyone wants them to be against each other and I totally see why but can I love my fierce dragon queen and still want Sansa to rule the North? Let me be they’re both awesome in different ways and had the show gone differently I think they could’ve been allies.

Also: I don’t give a shit about Jon. I simply don’t care what happens with him, but I don’t want him ruling the iron throne or the north
